    public class CodeInfoVisitor
extends JarVisitor
    Print class information with Apache Commons BCEL. Because BCEL represents the class as the real class file structure, it's able to extract more internals from it.

    The following are extracted:

    • Major and minor version of class
    • Name of source file it was compiled from
    • Constant pool
    • Package name
    • Class name
    • Extended superclass name
    • Implemented interfaces
    • Inner classes
    • Declared constructors
    • Declared fields
    • Declared qualified method signatures
